      <title>由于工资超出预期，日本央行押注三月加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/japan-s-wage-growth-beats-consensus-with-fastest-pace-since-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列报告和工资数据推高日元、债券收益率和隔夜掉期之后，有关日本央行将于本月自 2007 年以来首次加息的猜测激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/japan-s-wage-growth-beats-consensus-with-fastest-pace-since-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 23:32:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着日本利率押注的增加，股市暂停，日元飙升：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球股市在历史高点附近暂停，而日元则飙升，因为人们越来越相信日本央行最终将在三月份开始加息，这是最后一个这样做的主要央行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 22:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行试图安抚因思想自由争论而震惊的员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/ecb-tries-to-soothe-shocked-staff-in-freedom-of-thought-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执行董事会成员弗兰克·埃尔德森 (Frank Elderson) 于 2023 年 12 月 19 日星期二在德国法兰克福举行的新闻发布会上。欧洲央行表示，明年该地区银行的资本要求将从 10.7% 升至 11.1% %，反映宏观审慎政策的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/ecb-tries-to-soothe-shocked-staff-in-freedom-of-thought-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 20:52:00 GMT</pubDate>
